createRDA(address,address,address,uint25.details: create a new RDA contract and store the participants and the address

params.landlord: Can receive payments for damages up to the original deposit amount
params.tenant: The owner of the deposit that earns the interest
params.trustee: Earns a fee for enforcing off-chain contracts via multisig
params.trusteeFee: The flat fee for the trustee that is withheld; serves as compensation

returns.rdaAddress: the address of the newly created contract

getByParticipant(address).details: get all the RDA contracts that an address is involved in

params.participant: the address of the account to fetch the RDAs for

returns.contracts: an array of contract addresses that are associated with the participant
